      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand, something in the tier of Patek Philippe. i need help defining the 'ideal consumer' profile so we can nail the creative direction. can you give me a detailed breakdown of who this person is? like their lifestyle, where they travel, their hobbies, and also their typical ethnic and cultural background so we can make sure the imagery aligns with the brand's prestige. thanks.",
